sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>ForgotPasswordPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>PasswordResetRequestView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>PasswordResetConfirmView
    participant SER as PasswordResetRequestSerializer
    participant Model as PasswordResetToken
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Enter registered email
    FE->>API1: POST /api/accounts/password-reset/
    API1->>SER: PasswordResetRequestSerializer.validate(data)
    API1->>DB: CustomUser.objects.get(email=email)
    DB-->>API1: User found
    API1->>Model: PasswordResetToken.objects.create(user=user)
    Model->>DB: INSERT reset token
    DB-->>Model: Token instance
    API1->>Email: send_mail(subject, reset_link, user.email)
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK "Reset email sent"
    FE-->>U: Display "Check your email"
    Note over U,FE: User clicks reset link in email
    U->>FE: Enter new password with token
    FE->>API2: POST /api/accounts/password-reset/confirm/
    API2->>DB: PasswordResetToken.objects.get(token=token)
    DB-->>API2: Token instance
    API2->>API2: Validate token.is_valid
    API2->>DB: user.set_password(new_password)
    DB-->>API2: Password updated
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK "Password reset successful"
    FE-->>U: Redirect to LoginPage
